long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Goyral JD Data Extractor tool is a lightweight and powerful software for lead generation. 

JD Contact Extractor is software that can extract information such as business name, address, phone number, etc...

There are many places on the Internet that have many lead generation sources that you can use for marketing your product or service. Goyral JD Extractor is probably one of the best sources for getting information about local businesses as almost all companies are listed in JD.
